bicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016065, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "It is better to recite the following also…", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "In jumlo ko bhi adaa karna behtar hai…", "UrduDescription": "ان جملوں کو ادا کرنا بھی بہتر ہے۔۔۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1016066, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "Then Say: I am present seeking closeness to You through Muhammad and his progeny. I am present, I am present for hajj (May peace be with you, O Prophet and may the mercy and blessings of Allah be on you. In the name of Allah and by Allah and by His wish. Peace be with! With the Prophets of Allah and His Messengers. Peace be with! With the Messenger of Allah. Peace be with! With Ibrahim, the friend of Allah and all praise is to Allah, the Sustainer of the universes.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Allah! Mai haazir hu, mai Tujh se qareeb hona chahta hu Muhammad (s.a.w.a) wa Aale Muhammad (a.s) ke wasile se, mai haazir hu, mai Hajj o Umrah ke saath haazir hu haazir hu, aur yeh Umrah Hajj'e Tamatto ka Umrah hai, mai haazir hu. Ay woh Khuda jo jawaab dene ke qaabil hai mai haazir hu, ay Khuda! Mai haazir hu, jiska pura aur kaafi hona Tere ikhteyaar mein hai.", "Urdu": "اے اللہ! میں حاضر ہوں، میں تجھ سے قریب ہونا چاہتا ہوں محمدؐ کے وسیلہ سے، میں حاضر ہوں، میں حج و عمرہ کے ساتھ حاضر ہوں، حاضر ہوں اور یہ عمرہ حج تمتع کا عمرہ ہے، میں حاضر ہوں، اے وہ خدا کو جواب دینے کے قابل ہے میں حاضر ہوں، اے خدا میں حاضر ہوں، جس کا پورا اور کافی ہونا تیرے اختیار میں ہے۔", "RArabic": "LABBAYKA ATAQARRABO ELAYKA BE-MOHAMMADIN WA AALE MOHAMMADIN LABBAYKA LABBAYKA BEHAJJATIN WA U’MRATIN LABBAYKA WA HAAZEHI U’MRATO MUT-A’TIN ELAL HAJJE LABBAYKA LABBAYKA AHLAT TALBEYATE LABBAYKA LABBAYKA TALBEYATAN TAMAAMOHAA WA BALAAGHOHAA A’LAYKA.", "ArabicText1": "لَبَّیْكَ اَتَقَرَّبُ اِلَیْكَ بِمُحَمَّدٍ وَّآلِ مُحَمَّدٍ۔ لَبَّیْكَ لَبَّیْكَ بِحَجَّۃٍ وَعُمْرَۃٍ۔ لَبَّیْكَ وَہٰذِہِ عُمْرَۃُ مُتْعَۃٍ اِلَی الْحَجِّ۔ لَبَّیْكَ لَبَّیْكَ اَھْلَ التَّلْبِیَۃِ۔ لَبَّیْكَ لَبَّیْكَ تَلْبِیَۃً تَمَامُہَا وَبَلَاغُہَا عَلَیْكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "Ar